12 §445.1. Political party committees; election
13 A. Notwithstanding any other provision in this Part, if the presidential
14 preference primary is repealed, all elections for members of a state central committee
15 or a parish executive committee of a recognized political party shall occur at the
16 same time as the statewide presidential general election.
