18 Department of State that voters not affiliated with a political party may choose to
19 participate in its primary elections pursuant to R.S. 18:410.3(B), such notification
20 shall also allow unaffiliated voters to choose to participate in elections for the state
21 central committee and parish executive committee of the major political party. Any
22 voter who is not affiliated with any political party and who is allowed to cast his vote
23 on the ballot of a major political party shall cast his vote on the ballot for only one
24 major political party.
